runPreDeploymentEnvironmentChecks

protected boolean runPreDeploymentEnvironmentChecks(oracle.adf.share.ADFContext ctx,
                                                    boolean isProvisioningRun)
Checks for minimum required setup on the server, and application to run flexfields deployment. This is to identify missing or improper environment configurations that would cause runtime errors in flexfields deployment process. Also suggests action needed to rectify the problem with setup, where ever possible. Ignores any runtime errors while checking these configurations.

Parameters:
ctx - ADFContext of the present environment
isProvisioningRun - if the current deployment is triggered by provisioning flow
Returns:
true if any problems with setup cannot be identified. false if a problem with setup is identified.
